{
  "stem": "22869.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, he said something there in English, but I didn't understand a word he was saying, why he is taking me away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe he found out that my number wasn't right or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And bingo, he takes me back to that place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He releases me there, and I'm back in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm not going to sit and wait there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I pick myself up, and the world there really was in topsy-turvy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, everybody was moving about the best way you could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, the law was passed right away there in Austria and in Germany and in Czechoslovakia that anybody who was in a camp and he presents a number, and I had identification card from this place there-- has to be helped with any kind of-- of vehicle, train, free of charge.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- they had to pick up-- put up big stations from Red Cross to feed us and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I kept on going on foot and on-- and on hitching rides in, you know, with-- with-- with army vehicles, because very, very little private stuff was going on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then till I reached some train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the train-- it was just a question of going up and showing my identification DP number.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bingo, I was-- you know, I could travel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And little by little, I make my way till Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It took a while, I mean, a few days, nights.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the road we found people that we met from before, that you knew from before the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And needless to say that every time you found somebody you haven't seen them for years and that he is still alive, you know, you were hugging, you were kissing.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
